section.title: tsigkeyitem Datatype - Atomia DNS API
section.para:
tsigkeyitem is a struct with the following members:
Parameter
Type
Description
idintthe id of the change-row
namestringthe name of the zone this change-row applies to
changetimeinthe unix timestamp of this change (will be used as serial in SOA)
tsigkeynamestringthe name of the TSIG key for this zone
